&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Eight friends, Rewa, Nadiya, Inas, Bhim, Shreshti, Qarin, Lihan and Ednit, are sitting around a circular table, with their backs towards the centre.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;Rewa is sitting second to right of Nadiya.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D17.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2)&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Bhim back faces to the person who is immediate left of Rewa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D18.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 209px; height: 212px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;3)&amp;nbsp;Bhim sit in between Inas and Qarin and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Qarin is third to right of Lihan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Case(i) :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D19.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 252px; height: 213px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Case(ii) :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D20.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 209px; height: 230px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;4)&amp;nbsp;Ednit is second to left of Shreshti.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Case(ii) is doesn&amp;#39;t satisfy the conditon.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D21.png&quot; style=&quot;width: 285px; height: 227px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;there4; Here, &amp;#39;Shreshti&amp;#39; sits second to the left of &amp;#39;Lihan&amp;#39;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Shreshti&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>আট বন্ধু, রেওয়া, নাদিয়া, ইনাস, ভীম, শ্রেষ্ঠী, কারিন, লিহান এবং এডনিত, একটি বৃত্তাকার টেবিলের চারপাশে কেন্দ্রের দিকে পিঠ দিয়ে বসে আছে।</p>

<p>1) রেওয়া, নাদিয়ার ডানদিক থেকে দ্বিতীয় স্থানে বসে আছে।</p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D17.png" /></p>

<p>2)&nbsp;ভীমের পিঠ রেওয়ার ঠিক বামে বসা ব্যক্তির দিকে মুখ করে আছে।</p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D18.png" style="width: 209px; height: 212px;" /></p>

<p>3) ভীম, ইনাস এবং কারিনের মাঝে বসে আছে।&nbsp;</p>

<p>কেস (i):</p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D19.png" style="width: 252px; height: 213px;" /></p>

<p><span style="">কেস&nbsp;(ii):</span></p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D20.png" style="width: 209px; height: 230px;" /></p>

<p>4) এডনিট, শ্রেষ্ঠীর বামদিক থেকে দ্বিতীয় স্থানে বসে আছে।</p>

<p><span style="">কেস&nbsp;</span>(ii) শর্ত পূরণ করে না।</p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Savita_SSC_28-10-22_D21.png" style="width: 285px; height: 227px;" /></p>

<p>&there4; এখানে, &#39;শ্রেষ্ঠী&#39; &#39;লিহান&#39;-এর বামদিক থেকে&nbsp;দ্বিতীয় স্থানে বসেছে।</p>

<p>অতএব, সঠিক উত্তর হল<strong> &quot;শ্রেষ্ঠী&quot;</strong>।</p>

&lt;p&gt;The pattern followed here is:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Eight people, A, B, C, D, E, F, G and H are sitting in a straight line, facing north.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;Only three people sit to the right of A.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D3.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 94px; width: 364px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2)&amp;nbsp;Only one person sits between A and B&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3)&amp;nbsp;Only four people sit between B and D.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;F sits to the immediate right of D.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D4.png&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41); height: 95px; width: 364px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;5)&amp;nbsp;C is neither an immediate neighbour of B nor D.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D5.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 95px; width: 362px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;6)&amp;nbsp;E sits second to the right of G.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D6.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 95px; width: 364px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;7) H sits in the vacant place.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D7.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 95px; width: 363px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Clearly, three person are sit between H and A.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Three&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br><p>এখানে অনুসৃত ধাঁচটি হল:</p>

<p><strong>প্রদত্ত:&nbsp;</strong>আট জন ব্যক্তি, A, B, C, D, E, F, G এবং H উত্তর দিকে মুখ করে একটি সরল রেখায় বসে আছে।&nbsp;</p>

<p>1)&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">A-এর ডানদিকে মাত্র তিনজন বসে।&nbsp;</span><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D3.png" style="font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); height: 94px; width: 364px;" /></p>

<p>2) A এবং B-এর মাঝখানে শুধুমাত্র একজন বসে।&nbsp;</p>

<p>3)&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">B এবং D-এর মাঝখানে মাত্র চারজন বসে। F D-এর ঠিক ডানদিকে বসে।&nbsp;</span></p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D4.png" style="font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align); height: 95px; width: 364px;" /></p>

<p>5)&nbsp;C B&nbsp;বা D-এর নিকটবর্তী না।&nbsp;</p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D5.png" style="height: 95px; width: 362px;" /></p>

<p>6)&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">E&nbsp;G-এর ডানদিকে দ্বিতীয় স্থানে বসে।&nbsp;</span></p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D6.png" style="height: 95px; width: 364px;" /></p>

<p>7) H শূন্যস্থানে বসে।</p>

<p><img alt="" src="//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/23/08/F1_SSC_Arbaz_2-8-2023_D7.png" style="height: 95px; width: 363px;" /></p>

<p>স্পষ্টত,&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41);">H এবং A-এর মধ্যে তিনজন ব্যক্তি বসে</span></p>

<p>সুতরাং, সঠিক উত্তর&nbsp;<strong>&quot;তিন&quot;।</strong></p>

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Floors&lt;/strong&gt; : 1 (lowest) to 7 (highest)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1)&amp;nbsp;She does not live on an even numbered floor. (Either she lives on 1&lt;sup&gt;st&lt;/sup&gt;, 3&lt;sup&gt;rd&lt;/sup&gt;, 5&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; or 7&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; floor)&lt;/p&gt;

