		&lt;/tr&gt;
	&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2)&amp;nbsp;At least two floors are above and two floors are below the floor where she lives. (Thus, Anu neither lives at 1&lt;sup&gt;st &lt;/sup&gt;floor nor at 7&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; floor)&amp;nbsp; So case 1 and 4 are eliminated.&lt;/p&gt;

