		&lt;/tr&gt;
	&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3)&amp;nbsp;There are at least two floors between her and her friend who lives on the topmost floor. (So&amp;nbsp;Anu doesn&amp;#39;t lives at 5&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; floor) So case 2 is also eliminated.&lt;/p&gt;

