&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Logic:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;1 is subtracted&amp;nbsp;and 1 is added alternately to the position value according to the English alphabetic series.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;#39;SPEAKER&amp;#39; is written as &amp;#39;RQDBJFQ&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr;&lt;/p&gt;

